<td style="border-color: #000000;">
<p>The furniture is very <strong data-start="452" data-end="464">{modern}</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Delivers in 1–2 days</p>
<p>Special offer: free <strong data-start="510" data-end="522">{lamp}</strong> with every living room set</p>
